<i>There is no home</i>
<i>like the one you've got</i>

01:06:21.663 --> 01:06:25.827
<i>'Cause that home belongs to you</i>

01:06:25.934 --> 01:06:31.031
<i>Well, I was in trouble bad</i>

01:06:31.139 --> 01:06:34.597
<i>I was so confused</i>

01:06:34.709 --> 01:06:38.941
<i>I may not see in color, babe</i>

01:06:39.047 --> 01:06:43.507
<i>But I sure can feel blue</i>

01:06:43.618 --> 01:06:48.112
<i>I have been a lot of things</i>

01:06:48.223 --> 01:06:51.590
<i>They may not all be true</i>

01:06:51.693 --> 01:06:57.029
<i>My experience was so mysterious</i>

01:06:57.132 --> 01:07:00.192
<i>Till I met you</i>

01:07:00.301 --> 01:07:07.207
<i>Now the sun will rise in the east</i>

01:07:09.010 --> 01:07:15.540
<i>But I'm barking at the moon</i>

01:07:17.819 --> 01:07:22.051
<i>There is no home</i>
